{"type": "article", "id": 18328, "title": "为了美化自己的长相，我信了这14条（瞎扯的）面相理论 | 好奇心研究所", "description": "如果你有一个优点，那就使劲鼓吹这个优点；如果你没有任何优点，你可以说我长这样都是为了旺夫生财。——《如何与这个世界优雅相处》", "date": "2015-12-01T15:07:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 101671, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 94, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607130110ZYp21bHkXuBxw5cm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t1.  一白遮百丑，我白我不丑。（@甬道）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130059z9u5DJjxePqybKH7.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>2.  我不是脸大是婴儿肥☝️（@小红）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130101pA24oPT0JvqHwgKd.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56338028\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>3.  头大聪明。（@valga）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130101x3OCDTFiepoWr59s.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>4.  眼小聚光。（@Andrea_zxy）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130102DrVwCcgpHzWbsMIn.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.566\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>5.  一脸雀斑国际范。（@郝名人）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130103xJPVyOD0Nciuo2U8.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>6.  嘴唇厚性感（@陈帅）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130103mrlOUXZYxGH7eQw8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>7.  耳垂大有福（@南道以南）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130104bO5yRUhi9qz7JrlH.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t8.  有痘说明我还青春。（@TanSangYu）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130104J8FGiYqDdx0UpsN9.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>9.  <span>聪明绝顶（@enterprising）</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130105W5vtCfzy6Fn1pogJ.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.564\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>10.  大鼻子生财旺夫（<span>@</span>御弟姐姐Mayaya）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071301069rwhovZKJFfY0i7A.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.652\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>11.  大脑门旺夫（@杜薇薇）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071301074GBJfCr07bcmzwK8.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>12.  双下巴旺夫（@小红）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130108w3DyVXEixRHY4SdW.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>13.  圆脸旺夫（@橘小麦）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130109Z8dCanETrtYQBgmO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55568182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>14.  胖旺夫（@Cammi）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130109M0aZoxOAgrN9QKXz.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>编了那么多道理骗自己，不如对自己说一声：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>我觉得你就这样挺好看的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>爱谁谁！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<i><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\">好奇心研究所</a></i><em>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}